pull_request.body: Fixes failing downstream tests: This PR now ensures shared-lib versions of `liboqs` with its [changing SOVERSION number](https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/blob/3cf9849cc43545ad7fdeb3092a90f94ff1881680/src/CMakeLists.txt#L94)  are properly installed (when `liboqs` gets installed alongside `openssl`).
